{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Your_Story!.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a beautiful world above the clouds, you finally have a chance after having a tragic life, now living as a humble farmer. Your new responsibility is to nourish the souls with your food for those preparing to depart. Cultivate vibrant crops,forge connections with unique characters,and uncover the secrets of this ethereal world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you embrace your second chance?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/weather__2_.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the changing seasons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Things_You_Can_Do.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cooking isn\u2019t just a side activity\u2014it\u2019s an essential part of your adventure. With over 100 unique dishes to prepare, players will need to gather ingredients through farming, foraging, and purchasing from various vendors. Each dish requires players to participate in fun, interactive cooking mini-games, where precision and timing are key to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Cook.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Farming is a thrilling adventure with over 50 unique crops to grow. Players will\u00a0 plant, nurture, and harvest a variety of fruits, vegetables, and herbs.Careful attention to soil, seasons, and growth cycles is key. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Farming_Gif.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Building and Crafting offers endless possibilities. Players will gather materials, construct a wide range of structures, and craft tools, furniture, and decorations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Build_All.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fishing is a relaxing yet rewarding pursuit with a diverse range of fish to catch. Players will set traps in lakes, rivers, and oceans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Fishing.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Foraging is a rewarding activity that lets players gather a variety of natural resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Search through wild areas for herbs, mushrooms, berries, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Forage.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mining is an essential activity where players can uncover valuable resources beneath the surface. Extract ores to help you craft items and upgrade your tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Mine.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make friends with 40 townsfolk and unlock there backstories. And make right decision to have a romantic relationship with one of the 10+ Marriage  candidates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250100/extras/Talk.gif?t=1738943016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea